channel.title: Chaos Village Development Team
channel.description:
[center][size=18pt][b][u]Chaos Development[/u][/b][/size] Hi after making Haunted-Village and Haunted-Isle. I decided that i want to make a server using mostly 377 cache items because that's what i used for alot of things in my other servers. [size=16pt][u][b]Goals For Server[/b][/u][/size] [i][b]Full Woodcutting Full Fletching With Interfaces [size=14pt][b]Completed[/b][/size] Full Fishing or close to it Full Crafting if we can Full Smithing Full Cooking Full Mining Full Herblore Full Runecrafting Perfect Timers Must Train on Npc's Slayer Tower Awesome Client and much more.[/b][/i]
[size=16pt][u][b]Progress[/b][/u][/size] Added Full Fletching with interfaces.
[size=16pt][b][u]Coder Application Layout[/u][/b][/size] [code]Name: Position Applying For:(Client Coder or Server Coder) Experience: Proof of Experience: Form of Contact:(Preferably Msn) Why You Should Be Chosen:(no less then 3 sentences)[/code]
All applications will be looked at as soon as possible.
Forum in which we talk about development. [url=http://www.codersx.nationvoice.com/index.php]-Development Here-[/url]
Hope to be one of the best servers ever.
[b][u]Server Coders[/u][/b] Zanzibar --Open --Open --Open
[b][u]Client Coders[/u][/b] --Open --Open[/center]
Signed, Coder Quack
